    VALUES
        ('Purple Finch','Purple finches (Haemorhous purpureus) are small-sized sexually dimorphic birds. They are considered as one of the American Rosefinches and are related to house finch and Cassin Finch. Unlike their name, they do not exhibit purple shade.','t','2021-05-07 18:57:42.517205-07')
